Text: YPO NEWSLETTERYPO Newsletter Reminder from Blake Hogan Please submit any information you would like to share in the upcoming YPO Newsletter which will be distributed in July Possible topics Forum News Childrens Accomplishments Personal Professional Accomplishments Human Interest Stories Announcements Business News International News Also we would like to add a special section in the newsletter YPO Bookshelf We will feature books recommended by fellow YPO members wives or children Please let us know the title author of the book and if you wish added comments Please email the information to my assistant Vicky Lino at Vicky Lino American InfoSource Farnham Park Houston TX Phone Fax
